the use of broadcast television for communication amongscientists and engineers ..AJ. K. MACKENSIE
the science and engineering television journal is an experiment in the use of broadcast television for inter-professional communication .  coordinated by the aaas, under a nsf grant, 30 one-hour videotapes have been done in cooperation with 12 national societies .  evaluationindicates that the project is useful and a proposal isbeing considered for a second series with videotape distributionexpanded on a national basis .